        <tr>
          <td class="incompatible">RX-V575</td>
          <td class="incompatible">RX-V675</td>
          <td class="incompatible">RX-V775</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td class="compatible">RX-V1075</td>
          <td class="compatible">RX-V2073</td>
          <td class="compatible">RX-V3073</td>
        </tr>
      </table>
      <br>
      <p>Similar to HDMI Zone 2, this feature allows HD content to be played in another area of the home. The difference with Component Zone 2 is that it’s output is limited to Component video sources.</p>
      <p><img src="images/zone2-component.jpg" width="100%" ></p>
